   <body>
      <ol>
         <li>
            <p>From the App Launcher, find and open the <uicontrol>Power CLM</uicontrol> app. You
               can perform the same action in <uicontrol>Power CPQ</uicontrol> app as well. </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click the <uicontrol>Adobe Sign Admin</uicontrol> tab from the navigation bar.
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Send for Signature Components</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Add to Account</uicontrol>.</p>
            <p>
               <note type="note">
                  <p>Page Layout customizations can be applied to Contacts, Contracts, Opportunities, and Leads or any custom object as well. Select the appropriate option.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Page Layouts</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Edit</uicontrol> next to the Account Layout you want to customize.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Buttons</uicontrol> on the layout editor.</p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Drag and drop <uicontrol>Send for Signature</uicontrol> to the <uicontrol>Custom Buttons</uicontrol> section on the page layout below.
               </p>
            <p>
               <fig>
                  <image height="250"
                         placement="break"
                         href="../attachments/143887802/143887828.png"/>
               </fig>
            </p>
         </li>
         <li>
            <p>Click <uicontrol>Save</uicontrol>.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
   </body>
